      "title": "Karaitivu student ranks first in Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dwarakes, a student from Karaideo, has topped the medical field in Sri Lanka. It is also noteworthy that he is the son of Tamil Vannan, a medical scholar.",
        "He has made a record by getting the first place in the district and national level in the Tamil language source in the medical section. (a)"
